{"tid":1412963,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"想狗狗投降入嚟","createTime":"2019-08-05T08:25:30.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-11T16:06:38.000Z","uid":283741,"like":8,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"b1f255ce2115405fb79c7fbfbeb0a179d4e88b08","tid":1412963,"uid":283741,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-05T08:25:30.000Z","msg":"抗爭去到依家呢個階段，已經係短兵相接，野貓式突襲方向正確，但屬於出氣多過實際，而且風險高回報細，好難持續。所以小弟認為而家開始要做啲實質破壞，等狗狗復原時間無限期拖長。<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: large;\">1. 鑿爛水馬</span><br />\n<br />\n水馬係狗同其他政府建築物第一度防線，如果將所有水馬鑿穿注唔到水，呢堆只係廢膠，防線即破。<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: large;\">2. 癱瘓狗車</span><br />\n<br />\n冇咗狗車嘅狗狗，機動性大減，出動慢咗，前線就做多好多嘢。<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: large;\">3. 拆爛狗屋</span><br />\n<br />\n狗屋作用唔使多講，冇咗狗屋保護，狗狗好似赤身露體咁狼狽。而且狗骨庫唔再安全，獵物籠又變低設防，十八區狗屋都爛晒啲狗就好難捱。"},{"pid":"6b4eade1f4eac0b15b91b9884a4be3b6e24c87bd","tid":1412963,"uid":290815,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-05T08:26:18.000Z","msg":"[repost]香港點算？<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1412038\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1412038</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"f6932275b267d093c2bf21523b5d334b6f051db4","tid":1412963,"uid":283741,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-05T08:43:42.000Z","msg":"4. 挖掘馬路<br />\n<br />\n與其霸路，不如挖爛條路。路面凹凸不平，就算通番車都要慢駛，即係集體霸路。而重鋪要搞幾個星期，又係霸路，仲係政府協助。就算鋪完又可以掘過，仲令狗車難行。"},{"pid":"02b9c8e2bf515af7af9b681436f4c2fbb283c860","tid":1412963,"uid":283741,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-05T12:01:23.000Z","msg":"好重要好重要好重要"},{"pid":"f65fff7cdbcd2404aa6a3e9518c4ec06ab7c03ae","tid":1412963,"uid":283741,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-05T16:48:37.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"5261561116ad7687bd397d8998841b65551cab82","tid":1412963,"uid":245784,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-05T16:49:15.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"09cd73e75ec19b5d6cdb21a17d705e91470a3355","tid":1412963,"uid":238301,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-05T22:16:25.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"d57f0870f214eae954c9c3b995f08b5a480c3287","tid":1412963,"uid":120084,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-11T15:42:20.000Z","msg":"唔想殺人又想幫手既岩哂，破壞哂d狗既野"},{"pid":"554dde45dab58d843377c9f5d2c1b962b0e86bc4","tid":1412963,"uid":34063,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-11T16:04:16.000Z","msg":"邊個話我哋輸緊嘅我屌晒你哋老母！要嬴嘅全部同我入嚟！<br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/dBbvRS\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/dBbvRS</a><br />\n<br />\n推,所有掟磚同火魔法都係黑警扮示威者做既<br />\n緊記要事：<br />\n1. 射頭<br />\n2. 721無起訴<br />\n3. 狗扮示威者<br />\n4. 室內射tear gas<br />\n5.一米同胡椒球對人發射<br />\n6.罔顧安全,推人落電梯<br />\n7.黑警插贓嫁禍,塞管狀物體入示威者背囊<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/POs3Lz7.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FPOs3Lz7.jpg&h=6417b1c3&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"687a1d67cbcfef8d423bfa8e03a46ac7148dac83","tid":1412963,"uid":20658,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-11T16:06:38.000Z","msg":"721"}]}